            <title>[JDK-8316309] AArch64: VMError::print_native_stack() crashes on Java native method frame</title>
                <link>https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8316309</link>
                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>VMError::print_native_stack() either crashes on Java native method frame or fails to parse the stack beyond it.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Sample output:&lt;br/&gt;
V  [libjvm.dylib+0x62af1c]  pns2+0x18&lt;br/&gt;
