C  [libjava.dylib+0x4b0c]  Java_java_lang_ClassLoader_findLoadedClass0+0x3c&lt;br/&gt;
J 590  java.lang.ClassLoader.findLoadedClass0(Ljava/lang/String;)Ljava/lang/Class; &lt;a href=&apos;mailto:java.base@22-internal&apos;&gt;java.base@22-internal&lt;/a&gt; (0 bytes) @ 0x0000000128053874 [0x00000001280537c0+0x00000000000000b4]&lt;br/&gt;
V  [libjvm.dylib+0xe1e3c8]  Metaspace::contains_non_shared(void const*)+0x28&lt;br/&gt;
